comments: Williams III (BOS) does not establish himself in a legal position in Gobert's (UTA) path and delivers contact which affects his ability to defend.
Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in a screening position in Walker's (BOS) path and absorbs the contact.
Williams III (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in O'Neale's (UTA) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Smart (BOS) makes marginal hand to hand contact with Mitchell (UTA) on the perimeter.
Williams III (BOS) establishes his screening position in O'Neale's (UTA) path and marginal leg to leg contact occurs as O'Neale (UTA) loses his balance.
Brown (BOS) commits a take foul on Gobert (UTA).
Gobert (UTA) makes contact with Tatum's (BOS) head and contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Williams (BOS) and Gobert (UTA) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Tatum (BOS) commits a take foul on Gobert (UTA).
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in O'Neale's (UTA) path and gives him room to avoid contact.
O'Neale (UTA) has his hand extended forward and brushes Tatum's (BOS) leg prior to his upward shooting motion.
Walker (BOS) commits a take foul on Bogdanovic (UTA).
Smart (BOS) attempts a take foul and makes marginal contact to Mitchell's (UTA) side during his drive.
Theis (BOS) commits a take foul on Mitchell (UTA).
Brown (BOS) commits a take foul on Bogdanovic (UTA).
Bogdanonvic (UTA) places his hand to Brown's (BOS) front during his drive and marginal contact occurs.
